/p></div>\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-5 border border-outline-variant/50 shadow-[0_1px_3px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1),0_1px_2px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-10 pointer-events-none\"><svg class=\"w-full h-full text-primary fill-current\" preserveaspectratio=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 100 50\"><path d=\"M0,50 L0,34 C20,30 34,10 50,16 C65,22 78,6 100,10 L100,50 Z\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"relative z-10\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-surface-container flex items-center justify-center text-primary mb-4\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">conversion_path</span></div><div class=\"text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\">近30天转化率</div><div class=\"text-display-lg font-display-lg text-on-surface leading-none\">38.6%</div><p class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-3\">AI报价到下单的平均转化周期为 6.8 天。</p></div></div>\n</div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 xl:grid-cols-12 gap-6 mb-8\">\n<section class=\"xl:col-span-7 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/50 shadow-[0_1px_3px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1),0_1px_2px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] p-6\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-5\"><div><h3 class=\"text-title-sm font-title-sm text-on-surface\">客户画像</h3><p class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-1\">从行业、规模、采购节奏和协作阶段快速识别高潜客户。</p></div><button class=\"px-3 h-9 rounded-lg border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-lowest text-body-md text-on-surface hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors\">更新标签策略</button></div>\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5\">\n<div class=\"rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-5 border border-outline-variant/40\"><div class=\"text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant mb-3\">行业分布</div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-body-md mb-1\"><span>汽车零部件</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">31%</span></div><div class=\"h-2 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"h-full w-[31%] bg-primary rounded-full\"></div></div></div><div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-body-md mb-1\"><span>机器人与自动化</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">24%</span></div><div class=\"h-2 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"h-full w-[24%] bg-primary-container rounded-full\"></div></div></div><div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-body-md mb-1\"><span>新能源装备</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">18%</span></div><div class=\"h-2 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"h-full w-[18%] bg-secondary rounded-full\"></div></div></div><div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-body-md mb-1\"><span>医疗器械</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">12%</span></div><div class=\"h-2 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"h-full w-[12%] bg-tertiary rounded-full\"></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-5 border border-outline-variant/40\"><div class=\"text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant mb-3\">采购成熟度画像</div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4\"><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed text-on-primary-fixed-variant text-body-md\">标准化采购</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-secondary-fixed text-on-secondary-fixed text-body-md\">多工艺询盘</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-tertiary-fixed text-tertiary text-body-md\">高精度零件</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high text-on-surface text-body-md\">年度框架协议</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high text-on-surface text-body-md\">出口型企业</span></div><div class=\"space-y-3 text-body-md text-on-surface-variant\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span>高复购客户</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">612 家</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span>需要技术陪跑</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">185 家</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span>重点流失预警</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">27 家</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span>适合客服承接</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">428 家</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-5 border border-outline-variant/40\"><div class=\"text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant mb-3\">客户阶段分层</div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-body-md\">潜在线索</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">418</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-body-md\">试单推进</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">236</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-body-md\">批量合作</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">124</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-body-md\">战略客户</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">36</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-body-md\">需回访挽回</span><span class=\"text-error font-semibold\">19</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-5 border border-outline-variant/40\"><div class=\"text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant mb-3\">下一步运营建议</div><div class=\"space-y-3 text-body-md text-on-surface-variant\"><div class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-primary\">check_circle</span><span>将五轴加工高频客户分配给专属客服，减少报价往返。</span></div><div class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-primary\">check_circle</span><span>对 19 家流失预警企业发起回访，复核交期与品质投诉。</span></div><div class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-primary\">check_circle</span><span>将地址不完整企业推送给销售补齐开票与收货信息。</span></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"xl:col-span-5 space-y-6\">\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/50 shadow-[0_1px_3px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1),0_1px_2px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\"><div><h3 class=\"text-title-sm font-title-sm text-on-surface\">地址簿</h3><p class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-1\">客户主地址、工厂地址、仓储与票据地址统一归档。</p></div><span class=\"px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed text-on-primary-fixed-variant text-label-sm font-label-sm\">可同步至下单</span></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-4 border border-outline-variant/40\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\"><div class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">深圳智造科技有限公司</div><span class=\"text-label-sm text-on-surface-variant\">总部</span></div><div class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant\">深圳市南山区科技园科苑路 18 号 A 栋 12F</div><div class=\"mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high text-body-md\">开票</span><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high text-body-md\">合同邮寄</span><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high text-body-md\">默认对账</span></div></div><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-4 border border-outline-variant/40\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\"><div class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">苏州精密加工工厂</div><span class=\"text-label-sm text-on-surface-variant\">生产基地</span></div><div class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant\">苏州市工业园区金鸡湖大道 66 号 3 号厂房</div><div class=\"mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high text-body-md\">收货</span><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high text-body-md\">返修</span><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high text-body-